[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16610] updated labels in issue templates (#16610)
@Sheape:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16627] added integration test for associativity in power operator (#16627)
@app/dependabot:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16623] bumped tempfile from 3.21.0 to 3.22.0 (#16623)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16621] bumped actions/labeler from 5 to 6 (#16621)
