``cargo-audit``
 to speed up Security Audit workflow (#16615)
@weirdan:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16606] discarded 
``path add``
 input (#16606)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16590] fixed 
``std help externs``
 (#16590)
@blindFS:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16594] fixed panic on large duration number (#16594)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16591] fixed parser pitfall of redefining 
``def``
 (#16591)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16578] refactored LSP to clean up duplicated testing code (#16578)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16568] fixed LSP malfunctioning on unsaved files, empty 
``workspaceFolder``
 parameter, overlay use with prefixes (#16568)
@Bahex:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16593] made 
``for``
 loops lazy, no longer collecting their source (#16593)
@Jan9103:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16580] marked LSP sessions as non-interactive (#16580)
@andoalon:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16574] added 
``--endian``
 flag to 
``format bits``
 (#16574)
